getReserves(uint48[]).notice: It returns the reserves of the vaults specified in vaultIds

getUserBalances(address,uint256,uint256).notice: It returns the balances of the user in vaults [offset + 1, offset + numVaults].

getVaultStatus((address,address,int8)).notice: It returns the status of the vault. 0: InvalidVault - returned when the ERC20 tokens are not valid. 1: NoUniswapPool - returned when no Uniswap pool of the two tokens does not exist. 2: VaultCanBeCreated - vault does not exist and it can be created. 3: VaultAlreadyExists - vault already exists.

priceOfAPE((address,address,int8)).notice: It returns the price of the APE token. To get the price as [units of Collateral][per unit of APE], divide num by den.

priceOfTEA((address,address,int8)).notice: It returns the ideal price of TEA. To get the price as [units of Collateral][per unit of TEA], divide num by den.

quoteBurn(bool,(address,address,int8),ui.notice: If quoteBurn reverts, burn in Vault.sol will revert as well; vice versa is not necessarily true.
